pr_title: CATROID-1483 Select multiple objects to import from selected scene
pr_body:

- implementation of selecting multiple sprites for importing and merging
- refactoring of ImportSpriteHelper
- refactoring of tests for Merge/Import feature from MediaLibrary and Local
- New Dialog for importing multiple Sprites at once

New Tests that replace old ImportTests:
- SpriteFromLocalIntentDismissTest.kt
- SpriteFromLocalIntentTest.kt
- SpriteFromMediaLibraryIntentDismissTest.kt
- SpriteFromMediaLibraryIntentTest.kt

-ImportSpritesDialogTest.kt
-ImportVariablesManagerTest.kt
-RejectImportDialogTest.kt

https://jira.catrob.at/browse/CATROID-1483
If not merged beforehand this replaces also https://github.com/Catrobat/Catroid/pull/4613

pr_title: CATROID-1291 Select which object from which scene from another local project to add to the project's current scene

- a scene from which to choose an object, if it's a multiple scene project
- a specific object of that scene or the default scene
